      </prefercite>
      <arrangement id="aspace_fd8b313ebf0410dcd5b78b771c8a1ae7">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>Arranged chronologically.</p>  
      </arrangement>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_67040efbd10e149ed8c353ee99cd706e">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The materials include Latin documents which were read aloud at the commencement exercises of Yale College, 1753-1860. Each diploma contains a formal greeting from the president, faculty, and assembly by the head of the academy and a list of the candidates for degrees. Each document was signed and witnessed by the president and faculty representative and dated.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
